        "content": "<p>In case people are looking for it:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Bull. Amer. Math. Soc. 71 (1965), 40-106, DOI: <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1090/S0002-9904-1965-11234-4\">https://doi.org/10.1090/S0002-9904-1965-11234-4</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
