    {
        "content": "<p>I'm afraid a lot of categories would end up being called <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext mathvariant=\"bold\">Morphism</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textbf{Morphism}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textbf\">Morphism</span></span></span></span></span>...</p>",
        "id": 262626520,
